  ggpubr::ggboxplot(
    x         = "group"

    , shape   = "group"
  )
g1 %>% print()

# but it's better to think in terms of facets
t2 <- ds %>% 
  dplyr::filter(graphNum %in% c(12, 24, 40 ))
g4 <-  t2 %>% 
  ggpubr::ggdensity(
    x = "val"
    ,color = "group"
    ,fill  = "group"
    ,add = "mean"
    ,rug = TRUE
    ,palette = c("#00AFBB", "#E7B800")
  )+
  facet_grid(.~graphNum)
g4
